Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一天...终于来了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，还是要提醒一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.87,0:00:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看电视要保持距离唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.51,0:00:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到...连结婚证书都撕掉了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.58,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果还能想办法\N让她回到友纪身边就好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.88,0:00:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个就难了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那句话...我真吓了一跳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.62,0:00:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家...已经不回到老...\N友纪的身边去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.63,0:00:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回不去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，那张离婚协议书\N应该不是真心的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.86,0:00:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是名字已经签了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,友纪不也只是一时冲动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有那回事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.60,0:00:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直...躲着人家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.11,0:00:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是真的讨厌起人家了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这太不像莉采儿你了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常的你不是很能往前看的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.38,0:00:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚不也是想要帮助友纪\N想跟他和好的不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.62,0:00:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家这里是一阵的抽痛\N真的好想哭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次觉得这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.43,0:01:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.73,0:01:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来...寻找新的爱情会比较好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.17,0:01:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，干爹...把人家心中的...\N友纪的回忆去除掉吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.91,0:01:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她知道了真正的爱情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样帮她还原吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.45,0:01:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再看一下情况吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.75,0:01:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许还有可以说服的余地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这段期间\N你们去跟踪友纪的行动...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.46,0:01:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,状况坏到不能再坏的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起\N就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.38,0:01:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了\N也还是好喜欢好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一副臭脸\N也是那么迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.39,0:02:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.43,0:02:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧.........
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一．起．来．吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.13,0:02:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自那天以来的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论何时都还感觉得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.44,0:02:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管到哪里都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管做什么都好让人心动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都好像魔法师一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以让人高兴起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起 就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.14,0:02:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了 也还是好喜欢好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一副臭脸 也是那么迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧.........
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.05,0:03:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起来吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然只有莉采儿的东西不见了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,友纪又什么都不说就出门去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这到底是怎么一回事...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿她怎么了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生病了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谣传她已经离开岩城同学家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是怎么回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.09,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学! 莉采儿人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，岩城同学!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在叫你耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安~!\N(早~)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了好了，大家回到座位上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,圣本同学也快一点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.44,0:04:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也好好的学习吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,友纪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.22,0:04:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你真的完全不担心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不会想去找一找吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,友纪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平常一样上学去啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于有动作了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐小姐，你一个人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去唱卡拉OK啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺意外的嘛\N竟然会到这么喧哗的地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还以为她要出来找莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再看一看情况吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午安安~ 要到哪里去啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来不好的预感或许要成真了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好~! 回家吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连岩城同学都不来学校了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙好像每天四处玩的样子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.72,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家老妈说，在泡妞景点看过他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会老婆跑了，就自暴自弃了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦~? 已经要换跑道了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是真的还假的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,C班的松井说他也有看见啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也许会搬家也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦? 搬到哪里去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.74,0:06:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情来的突然，也还没有决定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.81,0:06:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...如果真是这样\N就搬到小龙家的旁边...吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个正好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犬吉拜托你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.76,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿完全不见人影...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你的鼻子可以带你找到她\N就把这封信转交给她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内容是...她误会了岩城同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 再继续下去也是没有意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.65,0:07:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼~\N看来...是我们太看得起他了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个分析...确定吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可惜...没有别的角度\N可以解释了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来的正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.75,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙这几天连找都不找你...\N每天只会来回于泡妞景点之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种家伙，马上忘记比较好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你选择回到这里，真是对极了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还原作业...开始吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.83,0:07:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各项资料做最终检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难不成...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干爹们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家有件事情想确认一下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请帮忙做个问卷好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这是...在做什么啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.84,0:09:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做这些事情...根本就挽回不了啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.48,0:09:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是怎么了...\N为什么...会这么寂寞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么...这么想哭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.27,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够把我和她连在一起的东西...\N没了...都没了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直...都在找人家吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.00,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然是好几年后的事...\N下次...我们一起拿去登记吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.47,0:11:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...人家...\N可以爆发个...乱七八糟吗...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦? 没有爆炸耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.74,0:11:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也好啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.24,0:12:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯! 老公!\N最喜欢你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡着了呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为响子小姐的胸部很舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小龙你真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩...希望能有九个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来帮你洗漂漂喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AO...l~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚刚叫了我的名字对吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次换犬吉帮我罗~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电影好不好看啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还好去看了\N感觉像回到了青春时代
